query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 b q1 s t1 tq1 u1 acc) */ select count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 10 AND q1.view_count <= 1000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('articles',
'difference',
'electrochemistry',
'everyday-chemistry',
'experimental-chemistry',
'past-tense',
'phrase-usage',
'reaction-mechanism',
'tense',
'verbs')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 10 AND u1.reputation <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('chemistry',
'ell')
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name ilike '%bene%'
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id;
